      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents. The interior has moderate wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car is functional but may require maintenance soon.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
